task.summary: Bug fixes for ActiveConstituentFluxes and ActiveDerivedConstituentsCard. Added function to compute the output waterbody, and used this to fix a bug.
Moved all classes to new packages to be compatible with the WAT source tree.
Changed load function to not require an input filename. The fully qualified path to w2_con.npt is used instead.

Added support for expanding and shrinking the cards in W2ControlList to accommodate changes in the sizes of Cards. The updateTable method in all cards with more than one data line have been updated to first clear the table (data lines) and then add rather than set each line of data to the table.
Added test for expanding and shrinking cards.
Added constructor to Parser that creates the W2 control file object. Renamed all of the non-Card classes to W2____.java
Bug fixes, new Bonneville 5 yr transition model, new folders.
Bug fixes, new data, new incomplete class to convert models using Excel date number to the legacy Julian day (day of year) format.
Implemented new W2Card in three classes and parser, and added some tests and documentation.
